  "version_pin_rationale": "libdrm 2.4.113 is the jammy security-pocket build. libdrm-common (Architecture: all) ships amdgpu.ids (the AMD GPU device-id database libdrm queries at runtime); without it libdrm.so.2's amdgpu_query_gpu_info() returns ENOENT and Hyprland's GPU-detection probe fails. Both .debs must be planted; the SONAME link libdrm.so.2 -> libdrm.so.2.4.0 is created by the build script (no ldconfig dep on host)."
